HEADWORD: Marmoration
<hw>Mar`mo*ra"tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>marmoratio</ets>.]</ety> <def>A covering or incrusting with marble;
a casing of marble; a variegating so as to resemble marble.</def>
